[Name] Freevo
[Summary] A Home Theatre PC Platform 
[Description] Freevo is a Linux application that turns a PC with a TV capture card
and/or TV-out into a standalone multimedia jukebox/VCR. It builds on
other applications such as MPlayer to play and
record video and audio.
